overview: Chock-full of archival footage, interviews with former players and coaches and more, this jubilant film celebrates the passion that surrounds one of college football's most prestigious programs: the University of Michigan Wolverines. Relive their many triumphs, including 11 national championships; thrill to their frequent victories over archrival Ohio State; and hear from the devoted fans themselves what makes Wolverine football so special.
title: Michigan Football Memories
